(2, 'Privacy Policy', 'privacy', '										<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">WE-GO! Car Rental acknowledges the importance of your personal information. We value your trust and strive to secure and carefully process the information you share with us. The collection, use and sharing of your information is only based on your permission or where allowed by law. Please read the following carefully to understand our views and practices regarding how we treat your personal information. By submitting your personal information to us you are deemed as agreeing to the use of your personal details as described in this Privacy Policy.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Our site may contain links to and from other websites, and if you follow a link to any of these websites, you do that at your own discretion and responsibility. Please note that these websites will have their own privacy policies and that we do not accept any responsibility or liability for those policies. Please check their privacy policies before you submit any personal information to those websites.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Google, as a third party vendor, uses cookies to serve ads on your site. Google’s use of the DART cookie enables it to serve ads to your users based on their visit to your sites and other sites on the Internet. Users may opt out of the use of the DART cookie by visiting the Google ad and content network privacy policy.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">What information do we collect?</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">We collect information from you when you register on our site, place an order, subscribe to our newsletter, respond to a survey or fill out a form.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">When booking or registering on our site, as appropriate, you may be asked to enter your: name, e-mail address, mailing address, phone number etc. We may additionally collect information about how you access our services, such as the Internet Protocol (IP) address used to connect your computer to the internet.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">If you give us information on behalf of someone else, you confirm that they have given you their personal information and that they have agreed to us using their personal information as set out in this document. If you give us sensitive information about yourself or others, you agree (and confirm that the relevant person the information is about has agreed) to us processing this information in the way set out in this document.<br>You may, however, visit our site anonymously.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">What do we use your information for?</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Any of the information we collect from you may be used in one of the following ways:</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">—To improve customer service – Your information helps us to more effectively respond to your customer service requests and support needs</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">—To process transactions – Your information, whether public or private, will not be sold, exchanged, transferred, or given to any other company for any reason whatsoever, without your consent, other than for the express purpose of delivering the purchased product or service requested.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">—To personalize your experience – Your information helps us to better respond to your individual needs</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">—To improve our website – We continually strive to improve our website offerings based on the information and feedback we receive from you</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">—To send periodic emails – The email address you provide for order processing, may be used to send you information and updates pertaining to your order, in addition to receiving occasional company news, updates, related product or service information, etc. Note: If at any time you would like to unsubscribe from receiving future emails, we include detailed unsubscribe instructions at the bottom of each email.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">How do we protect your information?</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">We implement a variety of security measures to maintain the safety of your personal information when you place an order or access your personal information.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">We offer the use of a secure server. All supplied sensitive/credit information is transmitted via Secure Socket Layer (SSL) technology and then encrypted into our payment gateway provider’s database only to be accessible by those authorized with special access rights to such systems, and are required to keep the information confidential. Our payment gateway provider is Sage Pay, and your details are collected securely using 128 bit SSL technology. The padlock image situated next to Insulation Shop Limited [GB] next to the address bar in your web browser shows that this technology is being used. You can read about FAQ about Sage Pay here.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">After a transaction, your private information (credit cards, social security numbers, financials, etc.) will not be stored on our servers.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">Do we use cookies?</span><br>Yes.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Cookies are small files that a site or its service provider transfers to your computer’s hard drive through your web browser that enables the sites or service provider’s systems to recognize your browser and capture and remember certain information. Cookies will not be installed, only if you allow.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">We use cookies to help us remember and process the items in your shopping cart and compile aggregate data about site traffic and site interaction, so that we can offer better site experiences and tools in the future. We may contract with third-party service providers to assist us in better understanding our site visitors. These service providers are not permitted to use the information collected on our behalf except to help us conduct and improve our business.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">Do we disclose any information to outside parties?</span><br>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer to outside parties your personally identifiable information. This does not include trusted third parties who assist us in operating our website, conducting our business, or servicing you, so long as those parties agree to keep this information confidential. We may also release your information when we believe release is appropriate to comply with the law, enforce our site policies, or protect our or others rights, property, or safety. However, non-personally identifiable visitor information may be provided to other parties for marketing, advertising, or other uses.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">Online Privacy Policy Only</span><br>This online privacy policy applies only to information collected through our website and not to information collected offline.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">Your Consent</span><br>By using our site, you consent to our privacy policy.</p>\r\n										'),
(3, 'About Us ', 'aboutus', '										<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">We offer a varied fleet of cars, ranging from the compact. All our vehicles have air conditioning, &nbsp;power steering, electric windows. All our vehicles are bought and maintained at official dealerships only. Automatic transmission cars are available in every booking class.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 52, 52); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">As we are not affiliated with any specific automaker, we are able to provide a variety of vehicle makes and models for customers to rent. O</span><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;\">ur mission is to be recognised as the global leader in Car Rental for companies and the public and private sector by partnering with our clients to provide the best and most efficient Cab Rental solutions and to achieve service excellence.</span></span>'),
(11, 'FAQs', 'faqs', '																																								<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word; position: relative; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85) !important;\"><div style=\"\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-size: 25px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;\">Claims and Accident</span></div><div style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word; position: relative; line-height: 1.5em;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; line-height: 1.5em;\">In case of damage or accident while driving any of our vehicle, first, reach out to the nearest Davao City Police station and file an Accident/Incident Report.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; line-height: 1.5em;\">The renter is responsible for any and all loss of or damage to the car resulting from any cause including but not limited to collision, rollover, theft, tire damage and vandalism, medical condition, flood, fire, hail or other acts of nature.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; line-height: 1.5em;\">Additionally, if we have the other party’s contact information, we will pursue them and/or their insurance company for our damages if determined they were at fault. However, our pursuit of the other party does not absolve you from your obligation with Car Rental Davao.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">Other charges that could be incurred by the renter:</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">Loss of Use:</span>&nbsp;As the renter, you are liable for the loss of the specific vehicle rented as detailed in our rental contract. When our car is unavailable to be rented, we are entitled to compensation for such loss.<br><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">Administrative Fee:</span>&nbsp;Car Rental Davao has a legal entitlement to return vehicles to pre-accident condition which includes the indirect damage of expenses related to administering a claim.</p></div></div></div>\r\n										\r\n										\r\n										\r\n										');

